SYLVANIA Smart WiFi products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.

After connecting Alexa to your SYLVANIA Smart WiFi products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "SYLVANIA Smart WiFi" app from the Google Play store or Apple App store;
(2). Register one SYLVANIA Smart WiFi account in our "SYLVANIA Smart WiFi" app;
(3). You need to have some SYLVANIA Smart WiFi devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our SYLVANIA Smart WiFi app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "SYLVANIA Smart WiFi" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from the Google Play store or Apple App store;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "SYLVANIA Smart WiF" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "SYLVANIA Smart WiF", and you'll be navigated to SYLVANIA Smart WiF login page;
(9). Input your SYLVANIA Smart WiF account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

 If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : 1-800-LIGHTBULB( 1-800-544-4828 )
